    <body>
        <p>If you are on one type of list and want to switch to the other kind of list (e.g., you are on a numbered list and want to change to bullets), right-click on the <span class="Emphasis">ol</span> or <span class="Emphasis">ul</span> structure bar to the left, and from the context menu select <span class="Emphasis">Type</span>. Then either click one of the list types or select <span class="Emphasis">Custom List Format</span> and choose a style from the submenu.</p>
    </body>
</html>